00:14:26.270 --> 00:14:29.120
So essentially I'm
really incentivized

00:14:29.120 --> 00:14:31.612
to avoid getting in
big pots with him.

00:14:31.612 --> 00:14:34.070
And I'm essentially hoping for
some of these smaller stacks

00:14:34.070 --> 00:14:37.490
to bust so that then, even
if I lose a big pot to him,

00:14:37.490 --> 00:14:40.130
I don't get the low
eighth place payout.

