00:15:13.330 --> 00:15:16.110
suited against ace-4, which is
basically great for everyone

00:15:16.110 --> 00:15:17.240
at the table.

00:15:17.240 --> 00:15:19.310
Because someone
busted, you're always

00:15:19.310 --> 00:15:22.120
cheering for people
who bust essentially.

00:15:22.120 --> 00:15:24.620
And I think also both
