00:15:34.130 --> 00:15:36.650
the ICM is very, very relevant.

00:15:36.650 --> 00:15:40.430
This Gerardocks guy,
he's not the shortest.

00:15:40.430 --> 00:15:43.130
He is one of the shortest, so
