00:16:40.010 --> 00:16:42.440
But this still
illustrates a point.

00:16:42.440 --> 00:16:44.540
So this guy, who
dealt a bit earlier,

00:16:44.540 --> 00:16:46.550
now he goes all in
for quite a lot.

00:16:46.550 --> 00:16:48.050
This is quite a big shove.

00:16:48.050 --> 00:16:50.540
And if you play by
my recommendations,

00:16:50.540 --> 00:16:55.320
I would never recommend
shoving this many bets.

00:16:55.320 --> 00:16:56.810
It's 24.

00:16:56.810 --> 00:16:57.845
That's quite a lot--

