So I mean I'm going to pick a
tournament that I [INAUDIBLE]..

00:20:00.010 --> 00:20:03.760
So it's in some sense not
the best pedagogical example

00:20:03.760 --> 00:20:06.481
because there is a
lot of selection bias.

00:20:06.481 --> 00:20:08.980
You know that I'm going to run
very good in the tournament I

00:20:08.980 --> 00:20:10.030
choose to show you guys.

00:20:10.030 --> 00:20:13.400
But if it's between that
and having be over in

00:20:13.400 --> 00:20:15.100
five minutes because I lost--

