He has to call, but I think it's
very borderline in either case

00:22:02.790 --> 00:22:05.380
because of ICM.

00:22:05.380 --> 00:22:08.020
So he does fold, though.

00:22:08.020 --> 00:22:11.630
So now ICM is a bit trickier
because now we're smaller.

00:22:11.630 --> 00:22:14.130
We're getting it all in with
any of these guys can really

00:22:14.130 --> 00:22:15.150
damage us.

00:22:15.150 --> 00:22:17.010
And there's still
two short stacks

00:22:17.010 --> 00:22:19.590
that everyone is
hoping will bust soon.

00:22:22.370 --> 00:22:25.450
So In this situation, I
could go all in and bully

00:22:25.450 --> 00:22:29.730
this Panpancrisy guy, but
